---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Privacy Policy — Praetor by Katafract"
  description="Praetor privacy policy. Your email, contacts, and calendar never leave your device. Offline-first, encrypted at rest, zero cloud sync."
  ogDescription="Praetor collects zero data. Your inbox, contacts, and calendar stay on your device. IMAP/SMTP encrypted sync. Nothing is ever scanned or profiled."
  section="prose"
>
  <link slot="head" rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css" />

  <div class="prose-header">
    <p class="prose-eyebrow">Praetor &mdash; Privacy Policy</p>
    <h1>Praetor Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="prose-meta">Katafract LLC &mdash; Coming with Sovereign &mdash; <a href="//privacy">All app policies &rarr;</a></p>
  </div>

  <div class="prose-body">

    <div class="callout">
      <p>Praetor is in development. The full Privacy Policy will be published when Praetor enters TestFlight. In the meantime, here's what we promise: your inbox, contacts, and calendar stay on your device. No cloud intermediary. No data scanning. No ad profiling.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>What We Know About You</h2>
    <p>Nothing. Praetor is built around offline-first design. Your email syncs via IMAP/SMTP to your device, where it stays encrypted at rest. We have no access to your mailbox, no copies of your messages, no view into your contacts or calendar events. Your data never reaches Katafract servers.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>If you have questions about Praetor's privacy practices, reach out:</p>
    <div class="contact-card">
      <h3>Privacy Inquiries</h3>
      <p>Katafract LLC</p>
      <p><a href="mailto:privacy@katafract.com">privacy@katafract.com</a></p>
      <p>We typically respond within one business day.</p>
    </div>

  </div>

</Base>
